{"tid":796362,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[仆街家姐] 有冇人都有個咁撚垃圾人渣嘅家姐","createTime":"2018-08-27T17:50:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T19:21:26.000Z","uid":173592,"like":14,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"363d53f988be80101a0d3536b766502f330cae44","tid":796362,"uid":173592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T17:50:48.000Z","msg":"有冇人同我一樣都有個好撚仆街對屋企冇盡過責嘅家姐⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n講下背景先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我家姐就黎25歲人 但係會考中五畢業之後就算有返工都從來冇交過家用<br />\n小妹就黎緊升year2 但係自從dse之後就冇再問屋企攞過錢 一直靠補習同part time黎自給自足<br />\n<br />\n記得由好細個，大概我小學個陣，佢已經成日都蝦蝦霸霸，成日都打我⋯⋯我小學個陣我家姐讀緊中學，小學成日都要做咩每日一篇，我做完都會玩下啲online game，有一次佢放學返到黎我仲用緊電腦，可能用得耐左啲，佢就開始催，我再玩多陣佢就開始郁手打我，後尾仲用指甲抓我塊面，我痛起上黎就踢左佢一腳，結果佢打得我仲甘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  最後連我本英文書都比佢撕爛埋，右邊面仲比佢抓到損左一大pat⋯⋯但係我屋企人都只係鬧左佢幾句就冇左件事，第二日返到學校啲老師同fd問我塊面做乜損左，我都仲要扮冇野忍住喊同佢地講係我自己唔小心整到，因為我唔想比人知我有個咁樣嘅家姐<br />\n<br />\n仲有一次我好心幫佢手一齊包書(我小三小四已經開始自己包，因為唔想麻煩呀媽)，但係佢就好似老馮咁，嫌三嫌四，唔該都冇句，結果我包唔到佢要求嘅咁樣，然後又比佢打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個次我比佢打到流鼻血，但係我唔敢同呀媽講，我驚佢會搵機會打多我一次⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n小學個時零用錢唔多，每日都係得1-2蚊，死儲爛儲，再加埋幫手摺下衫&rsquo;賺外快'，先儲到個幾百蚊，然後就鎖左係櫃桶，將條匙比呀媽keep，之後條匙唔見左，個櫃桶就開唔翻⋯⋯後來我係我家姐個櫃到搵翻條匙，開翻個櫃桶發現個幾百蚊唔見左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 於是就同左呀媽講，呀媽問我家姐係咪佢拎左，佢死口都話冇，到左最後件事都係不了了之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n *一直去到後尾幾年，去到我中三四左右，屋企耐唔耐都會出現啲錢不翼而飛嘅情況，無論係我父母定係我，銀包每隔一輪都會唔見咁啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每次父母問係咪佢偷錢，佢都一定唔會認，仲聲大夾惡，甚至乎仲屈我話係我偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屋企以前環境冇咁好，我又仲係小學，所以呀媽冇做野，得我呀爸返工養家。但係為左我呀姐，都死慳死抵儲筆錢比佢每個月去某間大型補習社補習。佢本身係band3中學(非歧視)，成績已經唔係好，諗住佢補下習會好啲，點知佢竟然拎啲補習錢去追星買品牌，冇去報補習，我呀媽一直都唔知，係有次諗住去等佢放補習先知佢根本冇補好耐⋯⋯但係佢唔單止覺得自己冇錯，仲覺得去補習係晒錢⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n-因為我呀姐太多仆街事蹟，打住我小學個陣發生嘅事先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  -"},{"pid":"2a6a91142732a5dd7ef45dd57207c26af08018ba","tid":796362,"uid":88862,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T17:56:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5fb8bf99ab144f8f7429a23e1740a57a9ebf3508","tid":796362,"uid":22692,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2a6a91142732a5dd7ef45dd57207c26af08018ba","tid":796362,"uid":88862,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T17:56:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T17:59:12.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6669109f7d0ecae590414691ac72ad45073ec0a","tid":796362,"uid":184233,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:00:22.000Z","msg":"So Long <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e9456e8be4b333d25b15490288e6dd1bbdf91a","tid":796362,"uid":173592,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a6669109f7d0ecae590414691ac72ad45073ec0a","tid":796362,"uid":184233,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:00:22.000Z","msg":"So Long <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:02:37.000Z","msg":"冇計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上世做得太多錯事 今世有個咁撚仆街嘅家姐"},{"pid":"566c62626a6a80c537d59c8782e2dbc26ba7f758","tid":796362,"uid":55032,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:11:10.000Z","msg":"支持家姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  樓主好撚柒"},{"pid":"ae36168e32c4e54173e98c4f74cec9128ec5622c","tid":796362,"uid":199820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:11:53.000Z","msg":"有同感<br />\n細個唔夠佢打成日比個pk家姐蝦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除咗騎牛牛之外仲會滴口水落我塊面度<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我喊、 嗌救命都佢唔會停<br />\n大個啲夠佢打；有次一嘢推開佢，跟住佢以後都唔敢打我<br />\n樓主可以試下還拖， 夠惡佢就唔敢搞你<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00e2c03f229809bc5050414f95c4952770f978ca","tid":796362,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:13:40.000Z","msg":"試下唔好一版打哂<br />\n吸引唔到人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"951a23abc8ff67ef14aeceec7dc9c17f77bf47f4","tid":796362,"uid":54051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:16:26.000Z","msg":"你家姐係咪mk妹, 依加仲係咪好正"},{"pid":"76a6a447c0ab120cfdc44c32e7b47b84290c92e5","tid":796362,"uid":173592,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"951a23abc8ff67ef14aeceec7dc9c17f77bf47f4","tid":796362,"uid":54051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:16:26.000Z","msg":"你家姐係咪mk妹, 依加仲係咪好正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:18:57.000Z","msg":"以前就mk妹 依家就死港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPepper lunch仲可以讀左做paper lunch添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你話正唔正"},{"pid":"ca0419452df4c5ac40f51f1729eaaa77a8a8faa9","tid":796362,"uid":173592,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:25:13.000Z","msg":"到左我中學我家姐就冇再打我，一黎我有能力反抗就二黎佢會考畢業之後返part time識左啲唔知咩人，成日唔返屋企去蒲去飲酒，任何人都搵佢唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要數呢幾年最仆街嘅事應該係佢走去同大耳窿借錢，仲用我電話number黎扮係我呀爸嘅，結果我每個月都會收到大耳窿電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d453a91965e410d276b7a805a29a0499d9e26b6","tid":796362,"uid":199984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca0419452df4c5ac40f51f1729eaaa77a8a8faa9","tid":796362,"uid":173592,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:25:13.000Z","msg":"到左我中學我家姐就冇再打我，一黎我有能力反抗就二黎佢會考畢業之後返part time識左啲唔知咩人，成日唔返屋企去蒲去飲酒，任何人都搵佢唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要數呢幾年最仆街嘅事應該係佢走去同大耳窿借錢，仲用我電話number黎扮係我呀爸嘅，結果我每個月都會收到大耳窿電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:35:14.000Z","msg":"同大耳窿講再打黎你就報警啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你家姐自己衰咪算仲要特登累屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac395eff7b64922234034840ec555ce4f6fde535","tid":796362,"uid":182195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca0419452df4c5ac40f51f1729eaaa77a8a8faa9","tid":796362,"uid":173592,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:25:13.000Z","msg":"到左我中學我家姐就冇再打我，一黎我有能力反抗就二黎佢會考畢業之後返part time識左啲唔知咩人，成日唔返屋企去蒲去飲酒，任何人都搵佢唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要數呢幾年最仆街嘅事應該係佢走去同大耳窿借錢，仲用我電話number黎扮係我呀爸嘅，結果我每個月都會收到大耳窿電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:37:45.000Z","msg":"世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1961355ec256c889670d9b9d9ec9f3ec3aac3b2d","tid":796362,"uid":2572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:38:56.000Z","msg":"女人都係睇樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我細妹生成一條廢柴都大把仔貼錢溝佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ba58b84a7f753cf0e220ba2b896b4c62199e637","tid":796362,"uid":2572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1961355ec256c889670d9b9d9ec9f3ec3aac3b2d","tid":796362,"uid":2572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:38:56.000Z","msg":"女人都係睇